Cell[TextData[{
 "The function ",
 Cell[BoxData[
 "VarD"],ExpressionUUID->"37ab9f6f-0024-42b1-82d5-227146e8f9c3"],
 " is designed for variation, the arguments of which specify the varied field \
and the derivative to be eliminated by IBP. \n\nThen the equation of motion \
and the stress tensor can be derived as follows."
}], "Text",
