  3.87273327596281*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"ee8602d6-01c6-4b07-8e9f-\
49eb35b9c7e4"],

Cell["\<\
If expand the equation of motion and stress tensor of F into A, and want to \
collect them back into F, the method of ansatz can be used as follows.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.874288878662991*^9, 
  3.874288954433188*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"599f4025-1944-491d-afdd-\
3c3ec6d627f4"],

